00:15:33,149 --> 00:15:35,935
"and thinking that thick water
the thinnest of air."

332
00:15:35,978 --> 00:15:39,373
"Since it is but well to be
on friendly terms

333
00:15:39,416 --> 00:15:42,376
"with all the inmates
