847
00:41:39,192 --> 00:41:41,847
-when Melville
was only one year old.
-MAR: Mm-hmm.

848
00:41:41,890 --> 00:41:44,197
But after meeting
Nathaniel Hawthorne,

849
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:47,243
